OK. I just watched the whole movie and would overall rate it around a 6/10 story wise.
Audio: 10
Video: 10
This movie is nothing I would go out of my way for. I'm not saying it's bad but it's definitely not a stunner. At points I was curious as to how and why so and so was happening, and I wasn't sure if the story even made sense. It just kind of felt like the story was winding on and on and didn't really tie back to itself in any significant way even though you could tell it should have.
Overall this is a movie that you should only download if you have the bandwidth or if you just feel like watching a movie.
